  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지, 카탈로그, 엽서</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fec676fc-dcab-44ef-aed2-7a1befbe3ffc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 등에</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-91a92ace-8742-45e2-8fc2-ea6f58e4d351\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d953589-e98c-4e69-a235-0d4b685bd4bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사용되는</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-de908d31-c09b-4f5b-b8a8-e50d4a7274c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-63057405-e9a4-440f-bdee-ce9cbd436a16\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b837efaf-eff6-46a9-a71f-a6535a6c6afb\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\">​</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-88cf46a9-26bd-413b-b9aa-f4c9a36008c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0c71d0a2-0f58-4ab1-902c-e7321befb3d7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6dc541c2-af74-4016-ba88-3032a1b6660f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2f405bab-96cf-4a56-ac8b-7b518f4488ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-44c6348d-e7f0-47ca-aa18-149503910cf0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6f1ccdb4-245f-499d-9adf-fcc90103dcbe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9172f667-8c0f-4acb-bba3-450b3be3cfb0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224033972961/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">금박 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">금박 인쇄는 보통 금색 박지를 열로 가열하여 종이에 흡착시키는 기법을 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5fd7a97-a136-49f3-85de-aa7c75737c99\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b6eb0d29-d743-4187-b507-fb45036f50e2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이에 금색의 박지를 흡착하여 접착시키기 때문에 잘 떨어지지 않고 인쇄로는 표현하기 힘든 반짝이거나 은은한 색상의 표현을 할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-61d5585e-9f63-4b0d-b1f5-0072eb8df890\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7c7bec88-8d5b-4500-852b-809a9911c176\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e6e35684-bfc5-45ae-8310-983620bdef9b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dddd0095-b805-4c45-afca-538d8bac2704\" style=\"color:#555555;\">박인쇄의 종류는 무척 다양합니다. 금박, 은박은 물론 청, 적, 먹 등 다양하게 색상을 구현할 수 있고 요즘은 홀로그램 등의 다양한 무지개 모양의 박도 유행하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9307afc-051c-42d6-9f23-e9c8ab4ee1c3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d21c7396-015a-4982-b409-5ff69d6bf1c1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0899b9ab-3dfb-4800-8836-58e1518cb353\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3077eb1-8118-4e34-bf5b-452b902ae00d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">금박만 해도 수십 종의 종류가 있습니다. 무광 금박, 유광 금박뿐 아니라 황금, 적금, 먹금 등 여러 가지의 다양한 색상의 박 종류가 존재합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3dd50a8a-cdc1-4672-8f56-b7b4eb505c09\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d845bd2e-9549-43a6-baa4-dca3fe933190\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-076557bc-d1a2-4a85-955e-f7c4af35ebc0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4e9755dc-7c40-42c9-a2e9-f9223319624b\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\">자세한 박 종류는 추후에 자세한 사진과 함께 블로그 글로 작성해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-07c75cd0-2787-43ca-9c60-637c187a4bef\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f81b5cef-c717-46c1-a320-71d40e63b092\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-949ca145-c0ac-4e91-8fdb-588b853bbf0a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224033972961/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-52946d01-8b25-47dc-ab09-fdddda5bb5ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ed2871e8-36cd-474d-a89c-b6820f80d0b2\" style=\"\">챗 GPT 발췌</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f433a2a1-d201-41d9-af6b-252852f6725c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224033972961/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6ebcba1b-c284-43f0-8c8b-f3efe16d8a33\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f54383b0-854b-492a-82ad-5250be766068\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d6cca104-4303-49f9-ad64-6d634e8d962a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요즘은 박인쇄를 처리하는 기법도 많이 발전하여 과거에 문제가 발생했던 얇은 선이나 디테일한 이미지 구현에서 약간은 자유롭게 처리가 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6f2c8bc-9902-4d1d-af84-14b3aefa05c6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-da746d90-b10e-402d-922d-24ea53e48533\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-adad3d5d-60b6-4801-b49f-f229c30ac8f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-036e56cd-a272-4ec1-b2e3-4878c90f489b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 얇은 선이 100% 구현되지 않으나 콜드 포일(Cold Foil) 방식의 UV 강화 처리 기법이 많이 각광을 받고 있어서 과거보다는 훨씬 더 디테일한 처리가 가능한 상황입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fa456da9-d1f8-4ccb-b32e-ef7bb7560998\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e641440c-9473-46af-bf16-eeda05927323\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da43e83a-f083-4003-a648-28db752caa03\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d615f30d-f1f6-45c5-bed0-f6310a408dc2\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>박인쇄 + 형압 기법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a6adba49-2aef-4b1d-82a1-70e0ec4e64a0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224033972961/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-da7b0792-fb14-4232-a38f-9a5edb52c425\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fe899d72-93a3-49ad-b24f-e8b5bb4b6814\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de78567b-b282-4e82-943a-be914665b85b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">박인쇄와 형압을 같이 하게 되면 실제적으로 핀트가 맞지 않아 보기 싫게 제작되는 경우가 많았습니다. 물론 이 역시도 100% 정확하게 맞춰드린다고 제안하지는 않습니다. 그러나 어느 정도의 오차를 감안할 정도의 동시 작업이 가능한 시대가 되었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c70b4f32-7d88-445b-97fa-3f6efbf16ea7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224033972961/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-871aba19-9a2d-4a1f-8579-f562cc5b40a7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc34d21b-8fe1-48a9-9cdf-f6ee8c4a0391\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5bb32e95-5aec-4c89-b50c-9e193df4eba9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">박인쇄와 형압을 함께 작업하게 되면 박인쇄가 더 튀어나와 보일 수 있어 강렬한 느낌의 박인쇄를 돋보이게 만들 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d074e4df-8d33-4c03-84d6-f293e7832e0f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f08b4155-47aa-4cad-9918-273dc248e16f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7f3e4fd0-c3a5-421e-880a-336683ac8b82\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224033972961/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-30bc9df0-edab-447d-9235-f5089609d11a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-626acaeb-f152-43f4-9b02-49b2eeed6966\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-41c477e2-2db1-4839-b15f-9d799323d510\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지처럼 약간의 이격이 발생하지만 크게 느끼지 못할 정도이며 금박 부분은 더 튀어나와 보이는 효과를 연출하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3a21517-a596-49d7-ab7c-1cec1fbd825b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-525fa2be-1863-431b-9559-880dbd98308a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ef8262d8-1625-4682-a112-b3f47277bd48\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224033972961/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b3b3ada-fa70-433f-bc5c-1374f2bade8b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8326b76a-2e53-4c30-a268-597ca677c72a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9eb98c12-b760-4fb8-9e43-7a119be0ff96\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 주의할 것이 형압은 인쇄 후면에 누름선의 자국이 남기 때문에 인쇄가 진행되면 누름선을 피해서 디자인해야 보기가 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5156c065-2510-4a2f-8f46-8e2dd12dcc1c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-02325a76-7f67-4e65-a5db-bd84331906c6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-37079f4d-ff9c-4e60-b066-97f564fb556e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-85fec279-651f-4544-a625-e11a764dea34\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이제 박인쇄를 하실 때 형압과 같이 작업해 보세요. 더욱 보기 좋은 효과를 보실 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d36580b2-cae6-42bc-8b08-d40c5bd00825\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2564a342-1eed-4d7f-b56a-e50a334a4a60\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a515eae-cb77-494d-9636-f9d9ff57f43f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e9f51d7-9edb-4999-b0bb-dd8d853018d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다만 너무 좁거나 얇은 디자인의 경우는 삼가 주시고 오차가 발생해도 크게 티가 나지 않는 경우 사용하십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F224033972961#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
